{"id": 1905, "genre": 1001, "title": "你是如何磨过deadline的？", "description": "死线前只要不干正事，全世界都变得特别有意思。是你吧！", "record_count": 2360, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170913101337USxgCArslJXbNu1V.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-14T03:00:19Z", "options": [{"id": 235520, "content": "如果还有明天", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714374}, {"id": 235522, "content": "看看手机继续睡 偶尔放首曲子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132172}, {"id": 235523, "content": "我妈说我就是下流呸，懒驴上磨屎尿多?不到最后不干正事", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059162}, {"id": 235782, "content": "熬夜拼死奋斗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983697}, {"id": 235529, "content": "再玩会手机我就去干活", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824497}, {"id": 235785, "content": "抓破头皮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 38243}, {"id": 235530, "content": "自我堕落，表面平静，内心翻腾，无奈的自我催眠告诉自己没什么大不了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132181}, {"id": 235532, "content": "玩无聊的彩色五子棋可以放任自己很长时间，在罪恶感和自我训斥下寻找完成任务的思路和动力", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065098}, {"id": 235788, "content": "越到最后越能激发效率潜能", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132777}, {"id": 235533, "content": "Deadline 前的一小时是我思路最清晰、头脑最冷静、选择最果断、效率最爆表的时候。心如磐石，万物不为所动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900231}, {"id": 235534, "content": "是deadtime吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679326}, {"id": 237587, "content": "就硬扛通宵啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139309}, {"id": 235543, "content": "刷微博，A站B站，知乎，数英，然后就……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819374}, {"id": 235545, "content": "?", "image": "img/option/option/20170914185113BuogvO6RE2e83kMQ", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132223}, {"id": 235547, "content": "有人说过，截止时间前是效率最高的时候，大概可以高到发明核弹吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869386}, {"id": 239643, "content": "人有多大胆，project拖多晚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117330}, {"id": 235548, "content": "拿预约表约客人打开手机打电话给客户，发现微博有好友艾特了，一上午时间就去看撸猫的视频了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940203}, {"id": 235549, "content": "拖延症严重", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918502}, {"id": 237085, "content": "不到开学前一天不写作业   最后一天想想还是游戏好玩哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137419}, {"id": 235550, "content": "玩会手机再开始吧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098150}, {"id": 236062, "content": "玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133647}, {"id": 235552, "content": "Research一切除了research的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965439}, {"id": 239136, "content": "临近一小时开动，前50分钟是冰，冷静精细化工作；最后10分钟是火，赶紧处理处理交了得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144554}, {"id": 235553, "content": "呀，首胜还没拿，然后…定个明天凌晨4点的闹钟起来做，肯定来得及", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130262}, {"id": 235554, "content": "抽支烟，喝点酒，再睡会儿！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818886}, {"id": 235557, "content": "幻想自己小宇宙爆发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122581}, {"id": 235558, "content": "GTD", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 235559, "content": "deadline就是最後期限", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950510}, {"id": 235562, "content": "一口气，电脑前，做到明亮，迎着朝阳，开车回家，洗个澡，化个妆，提案去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983267}, {"id": 235564, "content": "一直开学前最后一天补作业", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091748}, {"id": 235820, "content": "也没啥，就是隔五分钟刷一遍手机里的app", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132835}, {"id": 242220, "content": "想到DDL就心痛！总想往后拖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864958}, {"id": 235565, "content": "relax!虽然很捉急", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954783}, {"id": 235566, "content": "咖啡与paper伴我到天明", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1049978}, {"id": 235822, "content": "我就看完这个视频就睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231368}, {"id": 235567, "content": "没灵感 看会好奇心吧 噢？一点了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067897}, {"id": 235569, "content": "闹钟响了再睡五分钟特别香", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115002}, {"id": 235570, "content": "顺其自然", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132267}, {"id": 235571, "content": "I have so many things to do that I'm going to sleep.", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097882}, {"id": 235828, "content": "我背单词坚持打卡 就算到晚上23：52了也要打开APP快速又快速地过完然后打卡！死都不能断！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 884568}, {"id": 235573, "content": "先玩一会手机吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1100799}, {"id": 235577, "content": "基本上90%是在最后一晚11.59以后做好，同时，另有5%靠问同学，另有5%是为了100%完成度而强行瞎写填满的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228634}, {"id": 235578, "content": "死都要死埋距?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132296}, {"id": 235579, "content": "死线的时候就拿起自己的床上桌，再往自己太阳穴上抹风油精。小宇宙爆发，干完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746218}, {"id": 235580, "content": "还有一个月才截止，不着急，还有一周才截止，我不慌，还有一天才截止呢，明天啥都别弄就做些事儿了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132302}, {"id": 235582, "content": "我喜欢提前做好准备，所以先完成前期80%到90%的工作，然后剩下的一定要拖到最后半天才来搞?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132310}, {"id": 235583, "content": "说干就干！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541416}, {"id": 235584, "content": "不行太累了，我得买点东西犒劳自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680539}, {"id": 235585, "content": "拖到最后一刻，在拼命熬夜完成", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132320}, {"id": 235587, "content": "翻翻前男友微博\n“诶，这个评论他的女孩是谁”\n戳进去，疯狂翻女孩微博\n“再看看前男友的前女友吧”\n“再来看看前前男友”\n………………\n？？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132330}]}